---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import CarInside from "../../assets/images/about_car_inside.jpg";
---

<section class="about background">
  <div class="container about__container">
    <figure class="about__image-container">
      <Image class="about__image" src={CarInside} alt="Car interior view" />
    </figure>

    <div class="about__content">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-medium-normal">
        At Ddsgnr Auto Repair, our mission is to provide our customers with the
        highest level of car care and customer service. We believe that everyone
        deserves to drive a safe, reliable vehicle, and it is our goal to help
        make that a reality. With years of experience, state-of-the-art
        equipment, and a team of highly trained technicians, we are dedicated to
        restoring your car to its best condition. Whether you need routine
        maintenance or complex repairs, we are committed to getting you back on
        the road as quickly and efficiently as possible. Trust us to take care
        of your car – and you – every step of the way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .background {
    background-color: var(--color-kuno-greywhite);
  }

  .about__container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  .about__image-container {
    flex: 0 1 50%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about__image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 640px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about__content {
    flex: 0 1 50%;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .about__content p {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__container {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 48px;
      padding: 48px 24px;
    }

    .about__image-container,
    .about__content {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .about__image {
      height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
